\f6\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Purpose:
\f5\b0  This is what a programmer installs to 
\f6\b write and compile
\f5\b0  Java code.\
